  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the morphological and visual acuity outcomes
      associated with 1.5 mg bevacizumab versus 0.5 ranibizumab intravitreal injections for
      treatment of diabetic macular edema.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
