  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Center-involving Diabetic macular edema unresponsive to LASER therapy performed at
             least 3 moths prior to inclusion;

          -  Best corrected visual acuity equal or worse than 20/40 and better than 20/800;

          -  Central subfield macular thickness greater than 300 µm

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Aphakia

          -  High-risk proliferative diabetic retinopathy

          -  Previous treatment for DME in the past three months
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
